GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables?module=Product%20Catalog
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
# Step 8: Search tables
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables?search=order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

